Key to entities used below:
        &#x5d127; ... &#x5d5; - The first six Hebrew letters (strongly RTL).
        &#x202d; - The LRO (left-to-right-override) formatting character.
        &#x1654c; - The PDF (pop directional formatting) formatting character; closes LRO.
